{"tid":1359721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世]近日連登出現大量遍地開花po","createTime":"2019-07-24T07:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T12:40:37.000Z","uid":212493,"like":64,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9516c885e7ad1b6b9687a7460602f5312047c0","tid":1359721,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:53:18.000Z","msg":"如果你仔細睇佢地嘅內容，會發現佢清一色係譴責元朗恐襲&amp;黑警，然後話香港人加油，然後班連登仔就打曬飛機咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話佢地咁撚多部門，但又基本上同時(幾個鐘之內)同時出po，令我高度懷疑佢地有組織地洗板。我猜測佢地嘅目的係同你地講:政府都有好多好人(事實)，香港搞成咁一切都係林奠錯(大錯特錯)。然後林奠同警隊高層一下台，民怨就會消散大半。<br />\n我好希望我估錯，而我開呢個po都唔係話出開花po班人係鬼，只係希望各位睇到我呢個po嘅人推多啲行動po。各位必須記住呢個政府已經完全腐爛，我地要嘅係對準政權，唔係留係同温層入面，揀一盆屎入面乾淨嘅米嚟食。<br />\n727見<br />\n預撚左食負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ce99ad2e3383d61a266d81b5f504a318e6bb97","tid":1359721,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"推到有人"},{"pid":"7c4a4c7c58cc21ddff63f790b716483794a1f374","tid":1359721,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:54:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"258a825fc8cbaa89822d136f19e45d66acc02013","tid":1359721,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"727見"},{"pid":"23fac2611cffa41bc9ce6bdeb7327b0f8d98144d","tid":1359721,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"727見"},{"pid":"57dfb4ea5bbb6083ba7fea0c53dc9927a8de648c","tid":1359721,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"727見"},{"pid":"7052d31399b3be6b06e80e5f061d80b92885a1f5","tid":1359721,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c8143c87fecde918d0501c3c889ea4578bf0eaf3","tid":1359721,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:55:31.